
           Commands available from the Status Menu in Elm 2.5

 Key    Meaning
 ---    -------
  q,<return>
        Return to the index screen.

 ^L     Redraw screen.

  n     New and unread / old and unread / read.  Change with <space>.

  o     Restore original status of message as of entry to Elm or last resync.

  r     Whether the message has been replied to.  Change with <space>.

  u     Undo changes made this time in the status editor.

  x     Exit leaving folder untouched unconditionally.
